{{Infobox video game | image = Blackguards 2 cover art.jpg | caption = | developer = [[Daedalic Entertainment]] | publisher = Daedalic Entertainment | director = | designer = | producer = | programmer = | writer = | artist = | composer = | series = ''[[The Dark Eye#Video games|The Dark Eye]]'' | released = {{Unbulleted list|'''Microsoft Windows''', '''OS X'''|January 20, 2015|'''Playstation 4''', '''Xbox One'''|September 12, 2017}} | genre = [[Turn-based tactics]], [[Tactical role-playing game|tactical role-playing]] | modes = [[Single-player]] | platforms = [[Microsoft Windows]], [[OS X]], [[PlayStation 4]], [[Xbox One]] }}
'''''Blackguards 2''''' is a [[tactical role-playing game]] developed and published by [[Daedalic Entertainment]] for [[Microsoft Windows]] and [[OS X]] in 2015. It is a sequel to 2014's ''[[The Dark Eye: Blackguards]]''.
==Gameplay== {{empty section|date=August 2015}}
==Plot== {{no plot|date=November 2018}}
==Development and release== {{expand section|date=August 2015}} ''Blackguard 2'' was released for [[Microsoft Windows]] and [[OS X]] on January 20, 2015.<ref name="ign_date">{{cite web | url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/11/26/a-release-date-for-blackguards-2-has-been-revealed | title=A Release Date for Blackguards 2 Has Been Revealed | work=[[IGN]] | publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] | first=Wesley | last=Copeland | date=November 26, 2014 | accessdate=August 13, 2015}}</ref>
==Reception== {{expand section|date=August 2015}}
''Blackguards 2'' received average reviews from professional critics upon release. Aggregate review website [[Metacritic]] assigned a score of 74/100 based on 48 reviews.<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/blackguards-2 | title=Blackguard 2 for PC Reviews | work=[[Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=August 13, 2015}}</ref> IGN rates it a Good 7.8, commenting that it improved on its predecessor: "you can spend less time confused about the details, and more time fighting."<ref>{{cite web|last1=Johnson|first1=Leif|title=BLACKGUARDS 2 REVIEW|url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2015/01/16/blackguards-2-review|website=[[IGN]]|accessdate=22 November 2015}}</ref>
